        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Electric Vehicle Infrastructure Rebate Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to establish a rebate program to encourage investment in electric vehicle charging infrastructure. The program must provide rebates for certain expenses associated with electric vehicle supply equipment located at workplaces, multi-unit housing structures, and publicly accessible locations.</p>]]>
        </text>
